#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/init.lua:5
msgid "Glowstone"
msgstr "荧石"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/init.lua:6
msgid "Glowstone is a naturally-glowing block which is home to the Nether."
msgstr "荧石是一种自然发光的方块，存在于下界中。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/init.lua:32
msgid "Nether Quartz Ore"
msgstr "下界石英矿石"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/init.lua:33
msgid ""
"Nether quartz ore is an ore containing nether quartz. It is commonly found "
"around netherrack in the Nether."
msgstr "下界石英矿石是一种含有下界石英的矿石，通常在下界的地狱岩周围被发现。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/init.lua:45
msgid "Ancient Debris"
msgstr "远古残骸"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/init.lua:46
msgid "Ancient debris can be found in the nether and is very very rare."
msgstr "远古残骸可以在下界中被发现，而且极其罕见。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/init.lua:59
msgid "Block of Netherite"
msgstr "下界合金块"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/init.lua:60
msgid "Netherite block is very hard and can be made of 9 netherite ingots."
msgstr "下界合金块质地非常坚硬，可由9个下界合金锭制成。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/init.lua:99
msgid "Netherrack"
msgstr "下界岩"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/init.lua:100
msgid ""
"Netherrack is a stone-like block home to the Nether. Starting a fire on this "
"block will create an eternal fire."
msgstr "下界岩是一种类似石头的方块，存在于下界中，在这种方块上点火会永久燃烧。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/init.lua:119
msgid "Magma Block"
msgstr "岩浆块"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/init.lua:120
msgid "Burns your feet"
msgstr "灼伤你的脚"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/init.lua:121
msgid ""
"Magma blocks are hot solid blocks which hurt anyone standing on it, unless "
"they have fire resistance. Starting a fire on this block will create an "
"eternal fire."
msgstr ""
"岩浆块是炽热的固体方块，会对站在上面的任何人造成伤害，在这个方块上点火会永久"
"燃烧。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/init.lua:146
msgid "Soul Sand"
msgstr "灵魂沙"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/init.lua:147
msgid "Reduces walking speed"
msgstr "降低行走速度"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/init.lua:148
msgid ""
"Soul sand is a block from the Nether. It has a slowing effect when walked on."
msgstr "灵魂沙是下界的一种方块，走在上面时会减速。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/init.lua:199
msgid "Nether Brick Block"
msgstr "下界砖方块"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/init.lua:215
msgid "Red Nether Brick Block"
msgstr "红色下界砖方块"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/init.lua:221
msgid "Chiseled Nether Brick Block"
msgstr "雕纹下界砖方块"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/init.lua:227
msgid "Cracked Nether Bricks"
msgstr "裂纹下界砖块"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/init.lua:232
msgid "Nether Wart Block"
msgstr "下界疣块"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/init.lua:233
msgid "A nether wart block is a purely decorative block made from nether wart."
msgstr "下界疣块是一种完全由下界疣制成的装饰性方块。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/init.lua:247
msgid "Block of Quartz"
msgstr "石英块"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/init.lua:259
msgid "Chiseled Quartz Block"
msgstr "雕纹石英块"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/init.lua:270
msgid "Pillar Quartz Block"
msgstr "石英柱"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/init.lua:283
msgid "Smooth Quartz"
msgstr "平滑石英"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/init.lua:296
msgid "Quartz Stairs"
msgstr "石英楼梯"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/init.lua:297
msgid "Quartz Slab"
msgstr "石英台阶"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/init.lua:304
msgid "Smooth Quartz Stairs"
msgstr "平滑石英楼梯"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/init.lua:305
msgid "Smooth Quartz Slab"
msgstr "平滑石英台阶"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/init.lua:312
msgid "Nether Brick Stairs"
msgstr "下界砖楼梯"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/init.lua:313
msgid "Nether Brick Slab"
msgstr "下界砖台阶"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/init.lua:318
msgid "Red Nether Brick Stairs"
msgstr "红色下界砖楼梯"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/init.lua:319
msgid "Red Nether Brick Slab"
msgstr "红色下界砖台阶"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/init.lua:325
msgid "Nether Brick Fence"
msgstr "下界砖栅栏"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/init.lua:338
msgid "Glowstone Dust"
msgstr "荧石粉"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/init.lua:339
msgid ""
"Glowstone dust is the dust which comes out of broken glowstones. It is "
"mainly used in crafting."
msgstr "荧石粉是从破碎的荧石中产生的粉末，主要用于制作。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/init.lua:346
msgid "Nether Quartz"
msgstr "下界石英"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/init.lua:347
msgid "Nether quartz is a versatile crafting ingredient."
msgstr "下界石英是一种用途广泛的制作材料。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/init.lua:351
msgid "Quartz Material"
msgstr ""

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/init.lua:356
msgid "Netherite Scrap"
msgstr "下界合金碎片"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/init.lua:357
msgid "Netherite scrap is a crafting ingredient for netherite ingots."
msgstr "下界合金碎片是制作下界合金锭的合成材料。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/init.lua:363 mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/init.lua:384
msgid "Netherite Ingot"
msgstr "下界合金锭"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/init.lua:364
msgid ""
"Netherite ingots can be used with a smithing table to upgrade items to "
"netherite."
msgstr "下界合金锭可与锻造台配合使用，将物品升级为下界合金材质的物品。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/init.lua:368
msgid "Netherite Material"
msgstr ""

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/init.lua:373
msgid "Nether Brick"
msgstr "下界砖"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/init.lua:374
msgid ""
"Nether bricks are the main crafting ingredient for crafting nether brick "
"blocks and nether fences."
msgstr "下界砖是制作下界砖方块和下界栅栏的主要制作材料。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/init.lua:381
msgid "Netherite Upgrade Template"
msgstr "下界合金升级模板"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/init.lua:382
msgid "Smithing Template"
msgstr "锻造模板"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/init.lua:383
msgid "Applies to:"
msgstr "适用于："

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/init.lua:383
msgid "Diamond Equipment"
msgstr "钻石装备"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/init.lua:384
msgid "Ingredients:"
msgstr "原料："

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/lava.lua:7
msgid "Nether Lava Source"
msgstr "下界熔岩源"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/lava.lua:18
msgid "Flowing Nether Lava"
msgstr "流动的下界熔岩"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/nether_wart.lua:4
msgid "Premature Nether Wart (Stage 1)"
msgstr "未成熟的下界疣（第一阶段）"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/nether_wart.lua:5
msgid ""
"A premature nether wart has just recently been planted on soul sand. Nether "
"wart slowly grows on soul sand in 4 stages (the second and third stages look "
"identical). Although nether wart is home to the Nether, it grows in any "
"dimension."
msgstr ""
"刚种下在灵魂沙上不久的下界疣就是未成熟的下界疣（第一阶段），下界疣在灵魂沙上"
"会缓慢经历4个生长阶段（第二阶段和第三阶段看起来一样），尽管下界疣原产于下界，"
"但它在任何维度都能生长。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/nether_wart.lua:26
msgid "Premature Nether Wart (Stage 2)"
msgstr "未成熟的下界疣（第二阶段）"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/nether_wart.lua:48
msgid "Premature Nether Wart (Stage 3)"
msgstr "未成熟的下界疣（第三阶段）"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/nether_wart.lua:70
msgid "Mature Nether Wart"
msgstr "成熟的下界疣"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/nether_wart.lua:71
msgid ""
"The mature nether wart is a plant from the Nether and reached its full size "
"and won't grow any further. It is ready to be harvested for its items."
msgstr ""
"成熟的下界疣是一种来自下界的植物，已经长到最大尺寸，不会再继续生长了，它已经"
"可以收获其相关物品了。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/nether_wart.lua:105
msgid "Nether Wart"
msgstr "下界疣"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/nether_wart.lua:106
msgid "Grows on soul sand"
msgstr "生长在灵魂沙上"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/nether_wart.lua:107
msgid ""
"Nether warts are plants home to the Nether. They can be planted on soul sand "
"and grow in 4 stages."
msgstr "下界疣是原产于下界的植物，可以种植在灵魂沙上并经历4个生长阶段。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_nether/nether_wart.lua:108
msgid "Place this item on soul sand to plant it and watch it grow."
msgstr "把这个物品放置在灵魂沙上进行种植，然后观察它生长。"
